dps:narrativeDescription.gco:CharacterString:
The data product contains rather little information about lamp posts (class “Lamp post”), such as;
							  its identification, position, status (functional/non-functional), kind of light bulb, the owner/maintainer of the lamp post.
							Users of the data product reports information (class Comment) about whether the lamp post is working or not. This may be along with a detailed comment.
